    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and is being sold as-is, requiring significant mechanical and cosmetic attention. The engine currently runs roughly and the transmission exhibits noticeable slipping, indicating that major repairs or a full overhaul will likely be necessary. Externally, the body shows heavy rust, particularly along the door frames and wheel wells, along with several large dents and peeling clear coat. The interior has seen better days, with significant tearing in the upholstery, persistent odors, and non-functional electronics including the air conditioning and power locks. This car is ideal for a dedicated hobbyist looking for a project or as a source for salvageable parts.",
