      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 42
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Up for sale is a mechanically sound E46 M3, powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L straight-six engine featuring individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS variable valve timing. This example is paired with the desirable Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory-spec limited-slip differential. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including rear subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive VANOS service to ensure peak valvetrain performance. The chassis dynamics remain sharp thanks to refreshed bushings and a well-sorted suspension geometry. While the exterior displays minor road-going wear, the drivetrain remains potent, offering the visceral, analog feedback these chassis are renowned for.",
